parameters: \n<Zahin>Oh man... I'm gonna feel that tomorrow...
\n<Zahin>Oh shit though, there's a cave down here.
\n<Zahin>Okay, let's hope I can find a way out of here.
Would you like to return to the Command Tower?
\n<Goblin>Please... don't hurt us. We've given you all we've got.
\n<Goblin>We wish you luck human... please take down Krenko for us.
\n<Goblin2>We don't mean any harm I swear!
\n<Goblin>Yes... we... wanted no part in his raids... we don't want to hurt people.
\n<Goblin2>So he sent us down here... to mine... these purple substances...
\n<Goblin>Varmov he calls it... toxic substance that can be refined into drugs...
\n<Goblin>Please... don't hurt us... We just want to live...
\n<Zahin>Give me whatever stuff you got on you or I'll beat the shit out of you.
\n<Goblin>Please... all we just have is some bread and this card...
\n<Zahin>Look man, I'm going to kill the Krenko bitch.
\n<Goblin>Thank you! We will wish for your success...
\n<Goblin2>Here... this is what we have... maybe it will help you...
There's something here but it looks to be too destroyed to be useful.
